  "description": {
    "zh": "你好吗！这有笔生意，我从Mechanic那里订了一大批从西方来的枪械。枪是外国的，我还是更热衷于祖国产的枪，对老兵来说，本国货总是更合心意。好了，这是一把M1A，配备了Hybrid 46消音器和Schmidt & Bender PM II 1-8x24 scope瞄准镜，我需要你装备它在来一场艰难的行动。可不是打打SCAV那么简单，你需要给它来点真正的猎物。我会给你其中一把枪，你最好仔细欣赏一下！不要让它白白浪费了，这东西价值连城。如果你不幸弄丢了——那就是你自己的问题，自己想办法解决。我想测试一下这个配置如何。",
    "en": "Greetings! Here's the deal, I've ordered a bunch of western guns from Mechanic for my clients. Guns are foreign-made, I'm way keener on the Fatherland-made guns, native product is way closer to the old soldier's soul and all. So, the gun is an M1A with a Hybrid 46 silencer and a Schmidt & Bender PM II 1-8x24 scope, and I need you to give it a hard ride in action. And there's no way you just shoot some Scavs and call it a day, you will have to give it some real deal. I will give you one of these rifles, you watch after it! They cost a fortune, so if you lose it - that's your problem."
  },
